      • updateUserCredentials

        void updateUserCredentials(UserCredentials userCredentials)

        Parameters:

      • updateEnvironment

        void updateEnvironment(Environment environment)
        Update selected environment (backend) in sdk after initialization. All api calls are then executed on selected environment.
        Parameters:
        environment - contains URL address of selected backend.

      • getEnvironment

        Environment getEnvironment()
        Returns selected environment (backend) which is used for all api calls. Contains URL address of selected backend.
        Returns:
        actual environment (backend)
